<title>wǒ de míng zì yǐ jì zài tiān shàng 迦南1093</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ de míng zì yǐ jì zài tiān shàng, zài yě méi yǒu rén néng duó qù.
 yé sū jī dū zuò wǒ zhōng bǎo, xíng zǒu tiān lù chōng mǎn néng lì.
 méi yǒu yōu chóu bù zài kǒng jù, shèng líng yǒng zhù wǒ xīn lǐ.
 jiàn zhèng yé sū xuān yáng yé sū, huó shuǐ yǒng yuǎn yě liú bù xī.</lyrics>
</song>